data.description: So much new in this house over the past year: air conditioner, water heater, appliances, home rewire, gutters, garage door openers, pool liner and pool pump.  The roof was replaced in October of 2022 too.  This home has so much to offer to your family.  Inside you will see a neutral color palette throughout, making it easy to imagine yourself in this home.  Additionally, there is tile throughout, no carpet.  The living spaces on located one side of the house while bedrooms are on the other. Access to the rear of the home is right off the dining room, making it ideal for entertaining. The kitchen has quick access to family room or dining room.  Beautiful granite sits on gray cabinetry. Outside is a large pool and still plenty of yard space to enjoy.  The home is uniquely situated on a corner and in a cul-de-sac allowing plenty of parking for guests.
